## 0. The Role of Each Repo

| Repo | Role | What You Do |
| --- | --- | --- |
| [`AgentSocietyChallenge_w_CrewAI`](https://github.com/yuchieh/AgentSocietyChallenge_w_CrewAI) | **Design sandbox** | Design, iterate, and test your Multi-Agent Crew |
